Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx::_min_pkt

AGL_GMX_TX_MIN_PKT = Packet TX Min Size Packet (PAD upto min size)

Notes: Additionally reset when MIX<prt>_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
